  Kou3-mng5--e5 kong2, Li2 lai5 kau3 chiah oaN3! Jit8 to am3 lah! 
  Ki-tok-tou5 kong2, Hai7--ah! Na7 m7-si7 lam7-sam2 khun3 ti7 soaN e5 teng5-a2-lai7, i2-keng cha2-cha2 kau3 chit-nih8. Koh, na7 m7-si7 khun3 e5 si5 sit-loh8 bun5-pin5, iah8 khah cha2 kau3. In-ui7 tu2-a2 tit-beh poaN5-soaN e5 si5, chiah chai bun5-pin5 phah-m7-kiN3, chhe7 long2 bo5, kou-put-chiong hoe5-thau5 khi3 hit-e5 lam7-sam2 khun3 e5 sou2-chai7 chhe7; kai-chai3 koh chhe7-tioh8. Goa2 kau3 chit-tiap8 chiah lai5, si7 in-ui7 an2-ni. 
  Kou3-mng5--e5 kong2, Na7-si7 an2-ni, chit lai7-bin7 seng3 e5 peh-siN3, goa2 chhiaN2 chit8-lang5 chhut-lai5 thiaN li2 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7; phah-sng3 na7 thang, i chiu7 chiau3 chit keng e5 ka-hoat, beh chhoa7 li2 kap thong-ke e5 lang5 sio-kiN3. 
  Kou3-mng5 e5 lang5 chiu7 kong3-cheng, lai7-bin7 thiaN-kiN3 cheng siaN, chiu7 u7 chit8-e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 chhut-lai5, bin7-mau7 toan-chiaN3, koa3 sui2, mia5 kio3 Khun5-sin7 , mng7 Kou3-mng5 e5 lang5 kong2, Kio3 goa2 mih-tai7? 
  Kou3-mng5--e5 in3 kong2, Chit lang5 tui3 Chiong-bong5 siaN5 lai5, beh khi3 Sun5-soaN, in-ui7 kiaN5 lou7 ia3-sian7, koh jit8 am3--lah, beh hioh ti7 chit-nih8, mng7 goa2 ‘Thang mah?’ Goa2 u7 ka7 i kong2, beh chhiaN2 li2 chhut-lai5 khoaN3 chaiN2-iuN7. TaN li2 kap i kong2, chiau3 ka-hoat thang a2 m7-thang. 
  Khun5-sin7 chiu7 mng7 Ki-tok-tou5 tui3 tah-loh8 lai5, beh tah-loh8 khi3. Ki-tok-tou5 chiu7 chiong in3 kou3-mng5--e5 e5 oe7 lai5 in3 i. 
  Koh mng7 kong2, Li2 chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 chit tiau5 lou7? Ki-tok-tou5 chiu7 ka7 i kong2-beng5. 
  Koh mng7 kong2, Lou7--nih sou2 tu2-tioh8 si7 chaiN2-iuN7? Ki-tok-tou5 iah8 chit8-hang7 chit8-hang7 ka7 i kong2. 
  Au7-lai5 koh mng7 kong2, Li2 mia5 kio3 sim2-mih8? 
  In3 kong2, Goa2 mia5 kio3 Ki-tok-tou5; thiaN-kiN3 soaN-chu2 khi2 chit-e5 tian7, si7 beh chin2-che3 kiaN5 lou7 e5 sou2 khiam3-kheh, kiu3 in e5 gui5-hiam2, goa2 chiah it-hoat ai3 hioh ti7 chia. 
  Hit-si5 Khun5-sin7 thiaN-kiN3 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 oe7, iah8 hoaN-hi2, iah8 pi-siong. Chiu7 kong2, Goa2 tioh8 chhiaN2 ke-lai7 kui2-na7 lang5 chhut-lai5. Chiu7 chau2 kau3 mng5-kha, chhiaN2 Hian5-ti3 , Jin5-ai3, Keng3-khian5, saN lang5 chhut-lai5 kap Ki-tok-tou5 tam5-lun7. Tam5-lun7 liau2, chiu7 chhoa7 i kap ke-lai7 e5 lang5 saN-kiN3. Ke-lai7 choe7-choe7 lang5 chhut-lai5 ngia5-chih--i, ka7 i kong2, “Siu7 Chu2 un-tian2 e5 lang5--ah, chhiaN2 jip8--lai5.” SoaN-chu2 khi2 chit-keng chhu3, tiau5-ti7 si7 beh khoan2-thai7 chhin-chhiuN7 li2 teh kiaN5 lou7 e5 lang5. 
  Ki-tok-tou5 chiu7 tim3-thau5, te3 i jip8-khi3, i2-keng jip8-khi3 liau2, teh che7, chiu7 chhiaN2 i chiah8-te5. Hit-si5 e7-hng tng3 iau2-be7 pian7, cheng3-lang5 m7-kaN2 hoe3-si5, long2-chong2 chit8-sim ai3 siong5-se3 thiaN Ki-tok-tou5 e5 tai7-chi3. Chiu7 keng2 Keng2-khian5, Hian5-ti3, Jin5-ai3 kap i tam5-lun7. 
  Keng3-khian5 chiu7 kong2, Ho2 e5 Ki-tok-tou5--ah, goan2 i2-keng thiaN3-sioh li2, chiap-lap8 li2 hioh chia, lou7--nih8 sou2 tu2-tioh8 chiah-e5 su7-cheng5, chhiaN2 li2 long2-chong2 kong2-beng5, kiam2-chhai2 oe7 li7-ek cheng3-lang5. 
  Ki-tok-tou5 kong2, Che si7 goa2 sou2 ai3, li2 an2-ni kong2, goa2 put-chi2 hoaN-hi2. 
  Keng3-khian5 kong2, Li2 kiaN5 ThiN-lou7 si7 tui3 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3? 
  Ki-tok-tou5 kong2, Goa2 hiahN-si5 ti7 goa2 pun2-toe7, hi7-khang siong5-siong5 u7 thang kiaN e5 siaN teh pek goa2 chau2-khui. Hit-e5 siaN chhin-chhiuN7 ka7 goa2 kong2, na7 iu5-goan5 tiam3 ti7 pun2-toe7, tek-khak boe7 bian2-tit biat8-bo5. 
  Keng3-khian5 kong2, Li2 li7-khui pun2-toe7, siaN2-su7 kiaN5 chit-tiau5? 
  Ki-tok-tou5 kong2, Che si7 Siong7-te3 chi2-i3. In-ui7 goa2 hit-si5 chai gui5-hiam2, kiaN-hiaN5, m7-chai tioh8 siam2 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7; au7-lai5 u7 chit8-lang5 mia5 kio3 Thoan5-to7, khoaN3-kiN3 goa2 teh thi5-khau3 ngiauh8-ngiauh8-chhoah, i chiu7 chi2-tiam2 goa2 khi3 oeh8-mng5. Na7 m7-si7 an2-ni; goa2 eng2 boe7 tit-tioh8 jip8 hit-e5 mng5, kau3 taN iah8 boe7 kau3 chit nih8. 
  Keng3-khian5 kong2, Li2 lai5 chit--nih8 u7 tui3 Sek-si7 e5 chhu3 keng-ke3 a2-bo5? 
  Ki-tok-tou5 kong2, U7--ah, goa2 hit sou2-chai7 sou2 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 tai7-chi3, kau3 chit8-si3-lang5 m7-kaN2 boe7 ki3-tit. Tiong-kan u7 saN hang7 khah iau3-kin2--e5. Chit8 hang7, chiu7-si7 lang5 sim-koaN tit-tioh8 un-tian2 kam2-hoa3, mou5-kui2 sui ai3 beh biat8-bo5--i, Ki-tok iau2-ku2 po2-choan5--i. Chit8 hang7, chiu7-si7 lang5 tek-choe7 Siong7-te3, ti3-kau3 m7-kaN2 koh ng3-bang7 i e5 un-tian2. Chit8 hang7 chiu7-si7 lang5 teh khun3 e5 si5, bang7-kiN3 sim2-phoaN3 e5 jit8-chi2 i2-keng kau3, hit-si5 sou2 bang7-kiN3 chiah-e5 su7-cheng5. Chit saN hang7 chin si7 iau3-kin2--e5. 
